com.weemo.sdk.view

Interface WeemoScreenShareInFrame.OnWeemoScreenShareInFrameTouchListener

  • Enclosing class:
    WeemoScreenShareInFrame

    public static interface WeemoScreenShareInFrame.OnWeemoScreenShareInFrameTouchListener
    Interface definition for a callback to be invoked when a touch event is dispatched to this view. The callback will be invoked before the touch event is given to the view.
    Author:
    Simon Marquis

    • Method Detail

      • onWeemoScreenShareInFrameTouch

        void onWeemoScreenShareInFrameTouch(MotionEvent event)
        Called when a touch event is dispatched to a view. This allows listeners to get a chance to respond before the target view.
        Parameters:
        event - the event being performed.
